### Query Posts [GET /posts{?limit,skip,section,type,sortBy,filterBy,status,projectId,platform,author,moderator,bySimilarity}]

+ Parameters
    + limit (number, required) - Number of posts to return.

    + skip (number, optional) - Number of posts to skip.

    + section (enum[string], optional) - Section to filter by.
        If section is `project` then `projectId` and `platform` must be specified.
        If section is `author` then `author` must be specified.
        + Default: `all`
        + Members
            + `project`
            + `author`
            + `all`

    + type (enum[string], optional) - The type of the post to filter from the results.
        + Default: `all`
        + Members
            + `all`
            + `sub-projects`
            + `tutorials`
            + `video-tutorials`
            + `copywriting`
            + `blog`
            + `task-ideas`
            + `ideas`
            + `task-development`
            + `development`
            + `task-bug-hunting`
            + `bug-hunting`
            + `task-translations`
            + `translations`
            + `task-analysis`
            + `analysis`
            + `task-graphics`
            + `graphics`
            + `task-social`
            + `social`
            + `task-documentation`
            + `documentation`

    + sortBy (enum[string], optional) - Method used for sorting posts.
        This parameter has no effect when used with `bySimilarity`.
        + Default: `created`
        + Members
            + `created`
            + `votes`

    + filterBy (enum[string], optional) - Method used for filtering posts.
        When filtering by `review`, any posts that have already been reviewed will be
        excluded from the results. The `active` filter excludes any posts that
        haven't paid active and vice versa for the `inactive` filter.
        + Default: `any`
        + Members
            + `any`
            + `review`
            + `active`
            + `inactive`

    + status (enum[string], optional) - Status to filter posts by.
        + Default: `any`
        + Members
            + `any`
            + `pending`
            + `reviewed`

    + projectId (number, optional) - Retrieve posts by project ID.
        This parameter only takes effect when `section` is set to `project`.

    + platform (enum[string], optional) - Retrieve posts by platform.
        This parameter only takes effect when `section` is set to `project`.
        + Members
            + `github`

    + author (string, optional) - Retrieve posts by a specific author.
        This parameter only takes effect when `section` is set to `author`.

    + moderator (string, optional) - Moderator to use from moderated posts.
        When `status` is set to `pending`, the results will only return posts that
        have been moderated from this moderator with the `pending` status. When
        `filterBy` is set to `review` any posts moderated by this moderator will be
        excluded. Without those specific conditions, this parameter has no effect.

    + bySimilarity (string, optional) - Similar post search by title and body.
        When specified, `sort` is ignored as the results are sorted by the score of
        how close a post matches the content provided in this parameter.

