### Edit A Post [POST /posts/edit]

+ Request (application/json)
    Edits a post that _must exist_ on the Utopian platform. The `title`, `body`,
    and `json_metadata` do not have to be changed, allowing editing of only a
    single attribute. This end point has cross editing capabilities that are
    useful for moderators. Users lacking permission to cross edit will receive
    a `forbidden` status.

    + Headers

            session: secret-session

    + Attributes
        + author (string, required) - Post author.
            The author must not include the `@` prefix. The author must match
            the authenticated user. Otherwise the user must be a moderator to cross
            edit another user's post.

        + permlink (string, required) - Post permlink.

        + title (string, required) - Edited title of the post.

        + body (string, required) - Edited body of the post.

        + json_metadata (object, required) - Edited JSON Metadata of the post.

