### Update Or Review A Post [PUT /posts/{author}/{permlink}]

+ Parameters
    + author (string, required) - Post author.
        The author must not include the `@` prefix.

    + permlink (string, required) - Post permlink.

+ Request (application/json)
    Any user can use this endpoint to update their post in the database. This
    will synchronize the post in the blockchain to the database.
    
    To moderate post, the `moderator` parameter must be provided. The authenticated
    user must be a moderator otherwise a `forbidden` status is returned. If any one
    of the boolean parameters are `true` then the rest must be `false`. Otherwise
    the behavior of this API is undefined.

    + Headers

            session: secret-session

    + Attributes
        + flagged (boolean, optional) - Flag the contribution.
        + reviewed (boolean, optional) - Approve the contribution.
        + pending (boolean, optional) - Moderator is awaiting updates by the original poster to the contribution.
        + reserved (boolean, optional) - Reset all the parameters except for `moderator`.
        + moderator (string, optional) - Moderator of the contribution.

