## SteemConnect2 Proxy [/sc2]

This is a proxy of the SteemConnect2 API endpoints. The endpoints are
exactly the same, for example `/api/sc2/broadcast` is the same as
`https://v2.steemconnect.com/broadcast`. The endpoints documented below can also be
be found at [the SC2 GitHub repo](https://github.com/steemit/steemconnect). The
`session` header is required for authentication and is utilized to know which user
to broadcast as.

As previously mentioned, the API is fully capable of manipulating the STEEM
blockchain. This proxy allows universal access to the blockchain without
requiring multiple tokens on the client to access different parts of the API.

