### Broadcast Operation [POST /sc2/broadcast]

+ Request (application/json)
    Performs operations on the STEEM blockchain, such as voting and commenting.
    The operations that can be performed is restricted to the `posting` role.
    Responses vary based on the type of operation broadcasted to the blockchain.

    + Headers

            session: secret-session

    + Attributes
        + operations (array, required) - Array of Steem operations to perform.

+ Response 200 (application/json)
